  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "Cerys is preparing to lead the surviving tieflings onwards to Baldur\u2019s Gate. Shocked to have survived the Shadow-Cursed Lands, she finds herself taking responsibility for the others - in Zevlor\u2019s absence. It\u2019s not a role she ever wanted, but somebody has to do it. She\u2019s adjusting to a life without Zevlor, and briefly reflects on his surrender and presumed death.",
